[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0796","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0796.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0983","title":"Internic Whois Lookup 程序 whois.cgi 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Whois Internic Lookup 程序的 whois.cgi 脚本未正确过滤用户输入的域名参数，远程攻击者可通过在域名参数中注入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）实现命令注入攻击，进而执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Whois CGI 程序，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0983"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:27.610","remediation":"删除或禁用服务器上 whois.cgi 脚本，或对用户输入中的 `;|&$()` 等 shell 特殊字符进行严格过滤和转义，改用安全的 API 调用替代 system/popen 函数执行 whois 查询。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0983"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0796.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0797","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0797.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0984","title":"Matt Whois 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Matt's Whois 程序的 whois.cgi 脚本存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者通过在域名输入参数中注入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等），可导致任意命令在服务器端执行。该漏洞影响 Matt's Whois 相关版本，攻击条件简单且无需身份认证，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。用户应及时升级或替换该程序以消除风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0984"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:27.737","remediation":"立即停止使用 Matt's Whois 的 whois.cgi 脚本，改用维护中的替代品（如 Whois 3.x 或集成到系统 whois 工具）。如必须继续使用，需对 domain 参数做严格输入过滤，过滤掉 `;&|$` 等 shell 元字符，并对输入进行白名单校验（仅允许域名合法字符）。建议迁移至使用安全系统调用的现代 Whois 前端替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0984"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0797.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0906","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0906.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0832","title":"Linux NFS 服务器缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Linux NFS 服务器中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 NFS 服务发送特制的超长路径名请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出并执行任意代码。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 内核版本中运行的 NFS 服务，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害严重。建议用户升级至修复版本或限制 NFS 服务的网络访问权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0832"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.053","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.13 及以上版本，该版本修复了 NFS 服务处理长路径名时的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级内核，可在不需要 NFS 服务的系统上禁用 NFS 服务（如 `chkconfig nfs off`），或通过防火墙限制对 NFS 端口（2049/TCP/UDP）的访问。同时建议启用 ASLR 等内核防护机制作为纵深防御。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/1999/19991111","http://www.novell.com/linux/security/advisories/suse_security_announce_29.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh42-errata-general.html#NFS","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/782","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.4.20.9911091058140.12964-100000%40mail.zigzag.pl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0906.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0953","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0953.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1111","title":"Immunix StackGuard 缓冲区溢出安全绕过漏洞","description":"StackGuard（GCC 编译器缓冲区溢出保护扩展）1.21 之前版本存在安全机制绕过漏洞。攻击者可通过非线性攻击方式直接修改指向返回地址的指针，绕过 Random Canary 和 Terminator Canary 等栈保护机制，而非通过传统缓冲区溢出覆盖返回地址条目本身。该漏洞使得基于 Canary 的栈保护失效，远程攻击者在无需触发 Canary 检测的情况下即可实施缓冲区溢出攻击，严重威胁系统安全。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1111"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.603","remediation":"立即升级 StackGuard 至 1.21 或更高版本，该版本引入了 XOR Random Canary 保护机制，将 canary 值与返回地址进行异或绑定，有效防御绕过随机 canary 和终止符 canary 的非线性指针攻击。如无法立即升级，应审查代码中是否存在通过缓冲区溢出修改指针变量后指向返回地址的攻击面，避免使用 gets() 等不安全的字符串输入函数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94218618329838&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/786","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3524","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1111","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1111.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fpjr-9gj6-mc3v/GHSA-fpjr-9gj6-mc3v.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5fd10034-0e95-458a-8e9d-f6ddb2de6532.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0953.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0955","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0955.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1112","title":"IrfanView IrfanView32 图片文件缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IrfanView32 3.0.7 及更早版本在处理 Photoshop 图片文件头时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，当文件头中\"8BPS\"图像类型后跟随超长字符串时，触发栈缓冲区溢出。攻击者可构造特制的 .psd 图片文件，诱使用户在 IrfanView32 中打开，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1112"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.740","remediation":"升级 IrfanView 至最新版本（当前最新版为 4.6x 系列，已修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞）。临时缓解措施：避免打开来源不明的 Photoshop PSD 图像文件，可在文件资源管理器中取消 .psd 文件与 IrfanView 的默认关联。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://stud4.tuwien.ac.at/~e9227474/main2.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34066","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/781","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3549","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19610","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1112","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1112.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/781/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000869.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0955.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1520","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1520.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0985","title":"CGI City CC Whois 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"CGI City 公司开发的 CC Whois 程序中的 whois.cgi 脚本存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可在域名查询参数中插入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等），当脚本将用户输入传递给系统 shell 执行 whois 查询时，恶意命令被一并执行，从而导致任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 CC Whois 1.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0985"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:27.850","remediation":"立即停用或删除 whois.cgi 脚本，该程序已停止维护且存在命令注入漏洞。如确需 Whois 查询功能，更换为主动过滤 shell 特殊字符（如 | ; & ` $）的替代实现，或禁用 CGI 执行权限。在 Web 服务器层面限制 whois.cgi 的访问来源 IP 作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0985","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20433"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1520.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0587","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0587.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0821","title":"FreeBSD Seyon 2.1 本地溢出漏洞","description":"Seyon 终端模拟器 2.1 版本中存在本地权限提升漏洞。由于程序未对 -emulator 参数传入的程序路径进行有效验证，本地攻击者可指定恶意程序作为终端模拟器执行，从而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 及 RedHat Linux 4.0/5.1 等系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，需拥有本地访问权限方能利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0821"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.710","remediation":"移除 seyon 二进制文件的 setuid/setgid 权限：`chmod 755 $(which seyon)`，消除本地用户以特权启动任意程序的攻击面。建议彻底卸载 seyon（`apt-get remove seyon` 或 `pkg_delete seyon`），改用现代终端通信软件如 minicom 或 picocom。对于仍须使用的遗留系统，限制 seyon 可执行文件的属组并通过文件系统 ACL 控制访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/838","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/252"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0587.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0663","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0663.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0863","title":"FreeBSD Seyon 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统中 seyon 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置超长的 HOME 环境变量、或传递特制的 -emulator 及 -modems 参数触发，导致程序崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞亦可经由 GUI 界面触发，影响使用 seyon 通讯程序的 FreeBSD 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0863"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:12.860","remediation":"立即升级 seyon 至修复版本（升级至 2.20c 之后的补丁版本），或通过 FreeBSD ports 执行 `portsupgrade seyon` 命令更新到已修复的端口版本。FreeBSD 安全公告 FreeBSD-SA-99:06 已发布对应补丁，可从 https://www.freebsd.org/security/ 获取。如无法立即升级，作为临时缓解措施，应限制本地非信任用户对 seyon 的执行权限，避免将包含超长内容的 HOME 环境变量或特制的 -emulator/-modems 参数传递给 seyon 程序，同时使用 `chmod` 限制 seyon 二进制文件的执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0863"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0663.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0636","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0636.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0843","title":"Cisco Router NAT 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco 路由器在启用 NAT（网络地址转换）功能时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标路由器的 Telnet 端口发送特制的 FTP PORT 命令，导致路由器处理异常而崩溃或停止响应，造成正常网络服务中断。该漏洞影响运行 NAT 功能的 Cisco 系列路由器，攻击条件低（无需认证），危害等级中等，虽不导致代码执行，但可严重破坏网络连通性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0843"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:10.433","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 12.0(5.1) 或 12.1 及以上版本。如无法升级，可通过 ACL 限制外部发往路由器 Telnet 端口（TCP 23）的 FTP 流量作为临时缓解，或使用全局配置命令 `no ip nat service ftp` 禁用 NAT 对 FTP 协议的 ALG 支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0843"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0636.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0678","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0678.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0887","title":"FloosieTek FTGate 2.1 Web接口路径遍历漏洞","description":"FloosieTek FTGate 2.1 邮件服务器 Web 管理界面存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标发送包含 `../` 的恶意 HTTP 请求，绕过访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 FTGate 2.1 版本，攻击者可利用此漏洞获取系统敏感信息（如配置文件、密码文件等），为后续攻击提供铺垫。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0887"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:15.820","remediation":"立即升级 FTGate 至 2.2 及以上版本（该版本已修复路径遍历漏洞）。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器或反向代理层配置 URL 规范化规则，过滤 `../` 及 `..\\` 等目录穿越序列。限制 FTGate Web 管理界面的访问来源 IP，仅允许受信任管理网段连接。鉴于 FTGate 已停止维护且不再有安全更新，建议迁移至当前仍受支持的邮件服务器软件（如 Exchange、Postfix 等）以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD05261999.html","http://www.osvdb.org/1137","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19223"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0678.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0697","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0697.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0899","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 打印后台处理程序 DLL 注入权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 打印后台处理服务（Spoolss.exe）存在 DLL 注入权限漏洞。由于服务对打印提供程序注册表项的权限设置不当，本地认证用户可通过将恶意 DLL 指定为备用打印提供程序，从而以系统权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及所有 SP 版本，需要本地访问权限才能利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0899"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:17.310","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统，Windows NT 4.0 已终止支持且不发布安全更新。若无法升级，通过组策略或注册表限制本地用户对 Spoolss.exe 和打印提供程序注册表项 (HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Print\\Providers) 的写入权限，仅保留 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 完全控制权，移除 Users 组的写入权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ243649","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/769","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-047","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19594"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0697.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0917","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0917.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1065","title":"Palm HotSync Manager 3.0.4 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Palm Pilot HotSync Manager 3.0.4 在 Windows 98 系统中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当 HotSync Manager 运行于网络模式时，远程攻击者可向目标系统的 14238 端口发送超长字符串，触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Palm Pilot HotSync Manager 3.0.4 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1065"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:38.017","remediation":"立即升级 HotSync Manager 至 3.0.5 或更高版本（3Com 已承诺在新版中修复该漏洞）。在设置中将同步模式从「网络」切换为「本地串口/USB」，避免暴露 TCP 14238 端口。如必须使用网络模式，在防火墙层面添加规则阻止外部对 TCP 14238 的入站访问。由于 Palm OS 平台已停止维护，建议尽快将数据迁移至仍在支持中的现代设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94175465525422&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1065.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1065","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1065.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1065.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1065.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1065.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88443/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000854.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e7bd3e92452a8dc8da42d94ae3ba208936d5a5b9/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0917.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1056","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1056.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1340","title":"Hylafax Hylafax 4.0.2 faxalter 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Hylafax 4.0.2 的 faxalter 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 -m 命令行参数提交超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用后可获取目标系统的高权限。该漏洞影响 Hylafax 4.0.2 及之前版本，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，无需网络远程交互，危害等级较高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1340"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.947","remediation":"升级 Hylafax 至 4.1 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，移除 faxalter 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/faxalter）以消除本地提权风险，或限制可执行 faxalter 的用户组范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94173799532589&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/765","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19590","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1340.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1340","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1340.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1340.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v39v-9hrp-c85p/GHSA-v39v-9hrp-c85p.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1340.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--21456e6e-7fb1-48a2-9fee-105cd610c68d.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1056.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1200","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1200.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0896","title":"RealNetworks RealServer 管理工具缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"RealNetworks RealServer 管理工具中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向该工具的管理接口提交超长的用户名和密码参数触发缓冲区溢出，进而导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 RealNetworks RealServer 多个版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0896"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.937","remediation":"立即升级 RealNetworks RealServer 至 G2 版本或更高版本，该版本修复了管理后台认证过程中的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，应在防火墙层面限制对 RealServer 管理端口（默认 9090/TCP 和 9091/TCP）的访问，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 连接，并在输入验证层面限制用户名和密码字段长度。鉴于该产品已停止技术支持，建议迁移至更现代且受支持的流媒体服务器产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://service.real.com/help/faq/servg260.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/767","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19593"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1200.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1141","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1141.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1509","title":"Etype Eserv 2.50 Web服务器目录遍历漏洞","description":"Etype Eserv 2.50 Web服务器存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在URL中包含`../`序列绕过路径限制，读取文件系统中的任意文件。该漏洞影响Eserv 2.50版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，可能导致敏感信息泄露。由于该漏洞利用方式简单且影响范围明确，建议用户升级至最新版本或限制Web服务的文件访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1509"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-04","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Etype Eserv 2.50已停止维护，建议立即迁移至主流Web服务器（如Apache/Nginx）替代。若无法迁移，应在Web服务器或反向代理层配置URL过滤规则，拦截包含`../`或`..%2f`的请求路径，同时确保Web根目录外的文件系统权限最小化。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94183041514522&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94177470915423&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/773","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19601"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19601"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1141.toml"}]